sequenceDiagram
    autonumber
    participant U as User
    participant UI as Extension UI
    participant API as Backend API
    participant DB as SQLite Database

    Note over U,DB: Registration Flow
    U->>UI: Enter email and password
    UI->>API: POST /auth/register {email, password}
    API->>DB: Check existing user by email
    DB-->>API: User does not exist
    API->>DB: Insert new user with hashed password
    DB-->>API: User created
    API-->>UI: 201 Created + JWT token
    UI-->>U: Account created and session started

    Note over U,DB: Login Flow
    U->>UI: Enter email and password
    UI->>API: POST /auth/login {email, password}
    API->>DB: Find user by email
    DB-->>API: User record
    API->>API: Validate password hash
    API-->>UI: 200 OK + JWT token
    UI-->>U: Login successful

    alt Invalid password
        API-->>UI: 401 Unauthorized
        UI-->>U: Show authentication error
    end
